// NOTIF-04: Error fallback — send raw lead to Baptiste when pipeline fails
// Read lead data stored by main workflow's raw log node
const staticData = $getWorkflowStaticData('global');
const rawLead = staticData.lastLead ? JSON.parse(staticData.lastLead) : null;

// Parse error context from Error Trigger
const workflowName = $json.workflow?.name || 'Speed to Lead';
const errorMsg = $json.execution?.error?.message || 'Erreur inconnue';
const lastNode = $json.execution?.lastNodeExecuted || 'noeud inconnu';

// Build fallback SMS (keep under 320 chars — 2 SMS segments max)
let sms;
if (rawLead) {
  // Extract basic lead info for Baptiste
  const fields = {};
  for (const col of rawLead.user_column_data || []) {
    fields[col.column_name] = col.string_value;
  }
  const name = fields['FULL_NAME'] || 'Inconnu';
  const phone = fields['PHONE_NUMBER'] || 'pas de tél';
  const request = fields['demande'] || fields['message'] || '';
  const leadId = rawLead.lead_id || '?';
  sms = `LEAD PERDU [${workflowName}]\nErreur: ${errorMsg.substring(0, 60)}\nLead: ${name} | ${phone}\nDemande: ${request.substring(0, 60)}\nID: ${leadId}`;
} else {
  sms = `LEAD PERDU [${workflowName}]\nErreur: ${errorMsg.substring(0, 80)}\nDernier noeud: ${lastNode}\nAucune donnée lead disponible.`;
}

// Truncate total SMS to 320 chars (2 segments) as hard limit
return [{ json: { fallback_sms: sms.substring(0, 320) } }];
